no <silent><leader><space> <ESC>:let @/ = ""<CR>
"bang last command
nno <Leader>! q:kWgea!<CR>
"uppercase words
ino <C-u> <esc>mzgUiwza
nno <C-u> <esc>mzgUiwza
" Toggle [i]nvisible characters
nno <silent><leader>i :set list!<cr>
